
Changes from 4.2rc to 4.2
---------------------------

- Fixed bug #9315: Text entered into OE is lost with Firefox 2.0.
- Fixed bug: common element properties dialog doesn't work in IE browser.
- Added setting: ezdhtml.ini:[SystemSettings].RelativeURL
  Enables relative URLs (without host name) inside the editor.
  (related to bug #009663: wrong path to object_insert.png)
- Implemented: the default value of 'size' parameter in 'Insert object' dialog
  is defined by eZ Publish setting:
  content.ini:[ImageSettings].DefaultEmbedAlias
- Updated: Italian translation.